{
  "stem": "19596.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And one was a [NON-ENGLISH], he was-- the horses-- on the horses.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was next to him, and another guy behind me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now when he came to a latrine, we stopped, we opened up the top.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a container.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A liquid container.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Sit down.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we emptied the latrines and put the stuff in there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They let the sausages into the latrine from the factory, in plastic bags.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The plastic in the latrines, in plastic bags, chained up there, let it in, and I took it out on the other side of the factory.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the-- in the-- in the-- in the manure, in the shit inside.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the buckets, and then the buckets into the big container who was thrown by horses into the tank.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we went through the gate, and I had to-- I had to-- because I spoke German, they put me up, and I had to say so and so and so, number so-and-so, number so Scheisskommando asks to come in.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then the fellows were standing there like that, because we are all stinking.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then he poked sticks into it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What can he do with poking sticks into it?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He didn't find the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he said, in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Through.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that was it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then on in the camp, we had to unload it into one big-- one big ditch who was-- and then we took it out and we put it in the trousers and all that and brought it back.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Washed it and brought it back to the camp, to the-- to the barracks where the butchers were.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I got 50%.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
